false,"date":"26 Oct, 2017"},"required_age":0,"reviews":"\u201cIf you're looking for a thematically strong, clever traditional roguelike, look no further. Top stuff.\u201d<br>Adam Smith (Rock Paper Shotgun)<br><br>\u201cBest gateway drug into traditional roguelikes!\u201d<br>Epyon (Jupiter Hell, DoomRL)<br><br>\u201cThis is the work of someone who understands not only why roguelikes are such a long-lasting genre but also why they've been mostly stuck in a niche for nearly forty years: by identifying what actually works and separating it from what is just tolerated by inertia, Golden Krone Hotel is all gameplay and no busywork.\u201d<br>eb<br>","screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497800/ss_79a939f7f91971000abe7cfba8680b358a69aa5b.1920x1080.jpg?t=1673709340","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497800/ss_79a939f7f91971000abe7cfba8680b358a69aa5b.600x338.jpg?t=1673709340"},{"id":1,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497800/ss_bb0ff83d0e275626db31a139f1d520c6fc8df8f2.1920x1080.jpg?t=1673709340","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497800/ss_bb0ff83d0e275626db31a139f1d520c6fc8df8f2.600x338.jpg?t=1673709340"},{"id":2,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497800/ss_d00c30eeb2a913bb92b6e533cccd7ce91604f99a.1920x1080.jpg?t=1673709340","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497800/ss_d00c30eeb2a913bb92b6e533cccd7ce91604f99a.600x338.jpg?t=1673709340"},{"id":3,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497800/ss_f8a3fe17f2cdab9d3e048df01e2cc97f421b6ce0.1920x1080.jpg?t=1673709340","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497800/ss_f8a3fe17f2cdab9d3e048df01e2cc97f421b6ce0.600x338.jpg?t=1673709340"},{"id":4,"path